remixlab.bias.branch

Class GenericAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.core.Agent
      • remixlab.bias.branch.GenericAgent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericKeyboardAgent, GenericMotionAgent

    public abstract class GenericAgent
extends Agent
    A Agent extended with branches, see GenericMotionAgent.appendBranch(String), GenericKeyboardAgent.appendBranch(String).

    For branch handling refer to methods such as pruneBranch(Branch), branches(), branch(Grabber) and others. Branches enable the agent to parse bogus-events into GenericGrabber object Actions (see addGrabber(GenericGrabber, Branch)). Please refer to the Branch and the GenericGrabber documentations for details.
